{"ja424:0.1":"Jataka ","ja424:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","ja424:0.3":"Kaccanivagga ","ja424:0.4":"8. Adittajataka ","ja424:1.1":"“Adittasmim agarasmim, ","ja424:1.2":"yam niharati bhajanam; ","ja424:1.3":"Tam tassa hoti atthaya, ","ja424:1.4":"no ca yam tattha dayhati. ","ja424:2.1":"Evamadipito loko, ","ja424:2.2":"jaraya maranena ca; ","ja424:2.3":"Niharetheva danena, ","ja424:2.4":"dinnam hoti sunihatam”. ","ja424:3.1":"“Yo dhammaladdhassa dadati danam, ","ja424:3.2":"Utthanaviriyadhigatassa jantu; ","ja424:3.3":"Atikkamma so vetaranim yamassa, ","ja424:3.4":"Dibbani thanani upeti macco. ","ja424:4.1":"Dananca yuddhanca samanamahu, ","ja424:4.2":"Appapi santa bahuke jinanti; ","ja424:4.3":"Appampi ce saddahano dadati, ","ja424:4.4":"Teneva so hoti sukhi parattha. ","ja424:5.1":"Viceyya danam sugatappasattham, ","ja424:5.2":"Ye dakkhineyya idha jivaloke; ","ja424:5.3":"Etesu dinnani mahapphalani, ","ja424:5.4":"Bijani vuttani yatha sukhette. ","ja424:6.1":"Yo panabhutani ahethayam caram, ","ja424:6.2":"Parupavada na karoti papam; ","ja424:6.3":"Bhirum pasamsanti na tattha suram, ","ja424:6.4":"Bhaya hi santo na karonti papam. ","ja424:7.1":"Hinena brahmacariyena, ","ja424:7.2":"khattiye upapajjati; ","ja424:7.3":"Majjhimena ca devattam, ","ja424:7.4":"uttamena visujjhati. ","ja424:8.1":"Addha hi danam bahudha pasattham, ","ja424:8.2":"Dana ca kho dhammapadamva seyyo; ","ja424:8.3":"Pubbeva hi pubbatareva santo, ","ja424:8.4":"Nibbanamevajjhagamum sapanna”ti. ","ja424:9.1":"Adittajatakam atthamam. "}